AddressInfo.Title: Antelope Market and RV Park
AddressInfo.AccessComments: As an off-grid system, this unit is completely reliant on the sun. Due to this, the availability of power may vary and at off-peak times (early morning, eventing, at night) the battery will be quickly drained and may stop charging.

GeneralComments: This BEAM Global solar-powered charging station is located near the Antelope RV Park and Campground and behind the soon to be remodeled cafe. Two free charging stations are located on the solar unit, charging capability varies based on weather/ time of day. Full access restrooms are currently being built, and there is occasionally a food truck parked near this location.
